&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I tried setting the CamelLinkedIn.fields header, but this leads to further errors. The CXF 3.2.2 upgrade may be the culprit here. The tests run fine on Camel 2.20.x with CXF 3.2.1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
